gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: Multinational Geospatial Co-production Program (MGCP) dataset covering the 1°x1° degree cell between 124 and 125 longitudes and 7 and 8 latitudes.

gmd:statement.gco:CharacterString: 50k density feature extraction from monoscopic imagery using MGCP TRD v4.5.1. Ancillary source data used as needed to supplement the features not seen on imagery.
